<div style="text-align: center; margin: 10px;">
  <h2>复合查询统计</h2>
  <p>根据复合查询条件查询出信息并可导出抽样信息和检验信息。建立灵活的统计报表定制工具，方便用户根据实际需要定制报表生成条件和格式产生个性化报表。</p>
</div>
<ul class="nav nav-tabs">
  <li role="presentation" class="dropdown">
    <a class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
      筛选条件
      <span class="caret"></span>
    </a>
    <ul class="dropdown-menu">
      <li>
        <a>任务类别</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a>食品类别</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a>抽样地点</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a>生产单位</a>
      </li>
      <li></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
<div class="statistics-image">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-9" style="border-right: 1px solid #ddd;">
      <div id="main" style="width: 800px; height: 500px; margin-left: 20px;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3" style="height: 502px; overflow: scroll;">
      <table>
        <tr style="font-size: 16px;">
          <th style="padding: 10px;">抽样环节</th>
          <th style="padding: 10px;">不合格批次</th>
        </tr>
        <tr style="font-size: 12px;">
          <td style="padding: 10px;"><%= "餐饮" %></td>
          <td style="padding: 10px;"><%= @catering %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="font-size: 12px;">
          <td style="padding: 10px;"><%= "生产" %></td>
          <td style="padding: 10px;"><%= @production %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="font-size: 12px;">
          <td style="padding: 10px;"><%= "流通" %></td>
          <td style="padding: 10px;"><%= @circulation %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="font-size: 12px;">
          <td style="padding: 10px;"><%= "总计" %></td>
          <td style="padding: 10px;"><%= @circulation + @catering + @production %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
  $('body').scrollspy({ target: '#navbar-example' })
  var myChart = echarts.init(document.getElementById('main'));
  var option = {
    color: ['#3398DB'],
    title: {
      text: ''
    },
    tooltip: {},
    legend: {
      data: ['销量']
    },
    xAxis: {
      data: [
        "餐饮",
        "生产",
        "流通"
      ]
    },
    yAxis: {},
    series: [
      {
        name: '销量',
        type: 'bar',
        data: [
          <%= @catering %>,
          <%= @production %>,
          <%= @circulation %>
        ]
      }
    ]
  };
  myChart.setOption(option);
</script>
